{"tid":407575,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯] 住劏房不如返深圳住，含分析..","createTime":"2017-09-20T13:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T14:03:39.000Z","uid":82845,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0d02c4f1767d537bd5bb8949191015885df271c4","tid":407575,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T13:58:05.000Z","msg":"住劏房不如深圳住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n住劏房有乜唔好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.空間壓抑，四五千蚊淨係租到幾十呎劏房<br />\n2.自我形象低，影響心智發展<br />\n3.係屋企只能訓同玩手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4.唔敢叫朋友黎自己屋企驚比人笑比人可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搬返深圳有乜好? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.4500人仔有四百幾呎一房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.一般裝修會好過香港樓<br />\n3.生活簡便，可以隨便淘寶免郵費<br />\n4.住屋周圍環境一般比香港好好多，空間大好多<br />\n5.可以養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n6.得閒可以叫朋友返上去玩返一兩日。<br />\n7.食野可平可貴，平既一餐7蚊腸粉就夠飽，香港食腸粉閒閒地廿幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8.消費平，靠淘寶京東，對比香港消費平一半以上。<br />\n9.開住部一皮既80吋電視睇大量免費電影電視劇加個L形疏化真係爽爆，香港無過千呎屋都幾難做到，而且無大陸咁多劇戲睇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果係香港住得唔happy真係可以諗下返大陸住，要我住劏房?<br />\n我返大陸住係一個天堂一個地獄。<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟本係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">又要俾人話五毛啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcfde07977faa770efaa3ad017e97088239c68c","tid":407575,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}